      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "RIPPIN' PEDRO (7) has been in sparkling form, last time showing brilliant early pace and proving too slick around this track over 342m in 19.90, making it three wins on end. The form out of his last race has been franked. Hard to go past. ROLL ON COASTER (1) was midfield throughout and finished there last time when 4th (20.26) at this track. Form here at the trip sound including five wins. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and four minor placings to his credit. Key player if finds best. WITCHER ROSE (2) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (20.22) at this track. Has a good record here at this journey. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. A big run wouldn't surprise. TODD'S LUKA (4) must be included on latest effort.",
